# Developer Workflow: Complete User Manual

## 📖 Table of Contents

1. Getting Started (5 min)
2. Workflow Types & Selection (10 min)
3. Phase-by-Phase Guide (30 min)
4. Memory System (10 min)
5. Approval Gates (10 min)
6. Tools & IDE Integration (15 min)
7. Troubleshooting & FAQ (10 min)
