## 📚 Quick Reference

### File Structure
```
.workflow/
  workflow-orchestrator.md      ← START HERE
  
  instructions/
    core/                        ← Core principles
    workflow/                    ← Workflow details
    token-optimization/          ← Optimization
    developer/                   ← Dev-specific
    security/                    ← Security rules
  
  agents/                        ← 9 agent definitions
  
  hooks/                         ← Pre/post-phase hooks
  
  memory/                        ← Persistent decisions
    architecture/
    workflows/
    incidents/
    patterns/
  
  specs/                         ← Feature specifications
  
  snippets/                      ← Reusable prompts
```

### Key Documents
- **Start**: `.workflow/workflow-orchestrator.md`
- **Learn**: `.workflow/instructions/core/architecture.md`
- **Build**: `.workflow/instructions/workflow/lifecycle-routing.md`
- **Approve**: `.workflow/instructions/core/approval-rules.md`
- **Optimize**: `.workflow/instructions/token-optimization/`
- **Review**: `.workflow/instructions/developer/`

### Commands

**View current phase**:
```
See: workflow-orchestrator.md (routing section)
```

**Load spec**:
```
File: specs/[feature-name].md
```

**Check memory**:
```
Search: memory/ directory
Query: keyword search
```

**Run agent**:
```
Read: agents/[agent-name].agent.md
Follow: instructions in agent
```

