## 🎯 Summary

Welcome to the Developer Workflow! 

**Key Takeaways**:
1. Always start with `.workflow/workflow-orchestrator.md`
2. Follow phases in order (can skip some, not all)
3. Gates are hard stops (you can't bypass them)
4. Save decisions to memory (for team reuse)
5. Work is spec-first, not code-first

**Your Next Steps**:
1. Read the orchestrator (15 min)
2. Try one workflow (1-3 hours)
3. Give feedback to team
4. Help others learn the system

**Questions?** 
→ Check "Troubleshooting" section above
→ Or ask team lead

Happy building! 🚀
